reviewText:
Game has it's pluses & minuses. Overall, I'm giving it a positive recommendation.
-----------------------Pluses-----------------------
+ Has strong storyline;
+ Is Original (There ain't other similar games, at least at this moment);
+ Has a huge open world;
+ Has lots of fun things (Like you can go, play poker with others, or chess, do sidemissions, scan people & find out any info about them & lots of other stuff);
+ Cool weather (It's raining sometimes, which I like very much);
----------------------Minuses----------------------
- Has bad optimization. On Ultra it still lags even with FXAA (FPS jumping from 60 to 40), even on GTX 770, 16GB RAM & i7;
- Has some graphical downgrades (Like reflections ain't reflecting reality & they all have one image...);
- Low volume;
- Doesn't have Steam achievements;

All in all, game is just great excepting technical side.

